<h1>Below is PRE TAG</h1>
<p>Pre tag which preserves both line breaks and spaces , displays in a fixed width format(usually Courier)</p>
<pre>
     My Bonnie lies over the ocean.
     My Bonnie lies over the sea.
     My Bonnie lies over the ocean .
     Oh, Bring back my bonnie to me.
     
</pre>

     
